？</li>\n<li>李磊的喜欢的水果呢？</li>\n<li>动物呢？</li>\n<li>天气，家人们会第一个想到什么天气呢？画出来？</li>\n<li>想到小组聚会的时候，会想到什么呢？</li>\n<li>圣经故事呢？</li>\n<li>最后升华一下：想到耶稣，你会画什么？</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>得分最多的家人们得到彼此的默契大奖励。</li>\n<li>\n<p>想到耶稣，你会画什么？</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"默契大考验1\"\n        title=\"默契大考验1\"\n        src=\"/ice-breaking-game/static/b2b38159928cff8daf8248aca324fb8b/6a068/%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/ice-breaking-game/static/b2b38159928cff8daf8248aca324fb8b/f93b5/%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C1.jpg 300w,\n/ice-breaking-game/static/b2b38159928cff8daf8248aca324fb8b/b4294/%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C1.jpg 600w,\n/ice-breaking-game/static/b2b38159928cff8daf8248aca324fb8b/6a068/%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>到小组聚会的时候，会想到什么呢？</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 951px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 134.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n    